[normal]&#xa0;[bold]While government has started to address the problems, the recent Road Command Paper does not go far enough[bold]A new model of private investment is needed to improve the quality of the network and place the needs of the user at the heart of reform [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]There are crucial future steps government can take now to pave the way towards long-term reform of the roads network, while maximising current investment plans[bold]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Completing all feasibility studies for road and rail projects outlined in the Spending Round and committing to plans for delivery;
[normal]
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Conducting an audit of the state of the roads network and 
[normal]its costs to operate, so we 
[normal]have the means for a serious discussion about private finance after 2015.
